column12:
St. James needs a per trimester price per student in the next couple of weeks.  I told her I would need to get back to her on this.  My instinct is around $395 per student per trimester.

This is how they do electives:
    7th and 8th grade elective Fridays 10:45-12:15 Starting 8/30/2024
    Our Tech Club Demo day is scheduled on 8/23/2024
    School will collect all funds from the students then pay us
    They will advertise us this summer to make for a good demo day
    Robotics last year was somewhere between $250 and $300 per student according to the principal

Here are the trimester days in the school year:
    Trimester 1 August 21- November 15; All dates are Fridays, 10:45-12:15 10 Classes
    Trimester 2 November 18-March 7; All dates are Fridays, 10:45-12:15 9 Classes
    Trimester 3 March 10-June 7; All dates are Fridays, 10:45-12:15 8 Classes

No Make Up days for absent students.
Liability Insurance Copy to the School
Python Workshop Flyer designed for the school.
The Principal, Greg Hawkins, said he forwarded my email to Elisa to follow up.  I will email Thursday if I do not hear anything from her.
